{"tid":251194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有文字直播]2016-17 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附四強首回合","createTime":"2017-05-20T16:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T17:29:41.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20d40fe3a2aeb79299a6a0ec11bedde2b45020f2","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽四強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-5-21 7pm-12am *括號內數字為聯賽最終排名</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/IavHhyC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIavHhyC.png&h=4ced6be4&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YHww5ts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYHww5ts.png&h=06eb5cf2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(9)陳庭欣vs麥美恩(6)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NfArF5K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNfArF5K.png&h=44f0d3aa&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KwFUN98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKwFUN98.png&h=a5c194d0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(8)姚子羚vs譚嘉儀(模)(7)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">升班附加賽四強賽時為五小時，會員可於指定時段於以回覆投票方式揀選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">會員需清晰指出賽事投選女神，亦可選擇性投票予心水賽事。如會員同時投予兩位參賽者，將視為會員選擇和局，不投票增加該場比賽任何參賽者分數。<br />\n為免影響比賽公正性及體驗，會員<span style=\"color: red;\">不能再次回覆</span>以<span style=\"color: red;\">修改或增加投票選項</span>，請考慮好心水決定才作回覆投選。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"59eed994e66db4cf591c1a82ba405436873a3816","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:51:22.000Z","msg":"為方便會員投選,大家可引用以下列表以便發佈投票選項<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽四強首回合<br />\n2017-5-21 7pm-12am<br />\n陳庭欣vs麥美恩<br />\n姚子羚vs譚嘉儀(模)"},{"pid":"4e02f366e521c36c5e90ec4d8636b5cc860c8b76","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"其餘升班附加賽賽程請參閱下址<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e3b200dab2f325821a41f0ce858a54cf7224f5e1","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"兩場賽事既作客女神已經抵達比賽場館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca2c02a932e932e0aacaedf4c983a075e7dd09f","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"季內對碰,陳庭欣同麥美恩各自喺主場贏過1次,不過比較近期既係麥美恩主場贏過陳庭欣,不過臨時發揮至係最重要<br />\n<br />\n至於姚子羚同譚嘉儀,佢地2位喺季內交手2次,結果都係打成平手,Super!"},{"pid":"b9241e01b3ed8e1ceee04e6c3f0850726842016c","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"陳 麥 雙方開始進入比賽場地"},{"pid":"a5ed10ea8e2e0e4f333865f0040d0924563c2aed","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"姚 譚 雙方開始進入比賽場地"},{"pid":"33bfb3c9788d93efc21bce8e4342788da5506591","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"兩場比賽既裁判都鳴笛啦，賽事開始"},{"pid":"2d21f1576fdad4206725168fd821bb4071bb2422","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"5' 兩場比賽都仲係試探緊,未有實質埋門"},{"pid":"7142429cc836818dc1552f7ff126cf8489711c9c","tid":251194,"uid":92376,"like":0,"disl